import sys

h1, h2 = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())
a, b = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())

day = 0

while h1 < h2:
    h1 += a
    day += 1
    h1 -= b
    day += 1

if h1 == h2:
    print(day)
else:
    print(-1)
